---
title: Chicken, Haloumi & Fluffy Veggie Freekah with Roasted Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Whip up a chicken, haloumi and freekeh extravaganza in four easy steps. Drizzle over some honey to coat the haloumi and toss the
freekeh with some carrot and courgette and it will look and taste like you’ve been cooking for hours.

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with freekah due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651d7e19a19829649acd92b9-154097f3.jpeg
